? matches a single character.

* matches zero or more characters, excluding /.

** matches zero or more directories in a path.

The pattern "/events/**" matches "/events", "/events/", "/
events/1", and "/events/1/form?test=1"; it does not match "/
events123".

The pattern "/events*" matches "/events", and "/events123"; it
does not match "/events/" or "/events/1".

The pattern "/events*/**" matches "/events", "/events/", "/
events/1","/events123", "/events123/456", and "/events/1/
form?test=1".
